Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.44,0:00:04.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There is no shape to flowing water.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.06,0:00:05.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There is no figure to flowing wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.65,0:00:07.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter the case, the deduction is free.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.69,0:00:09.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Today's stage is a plateau hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.40,0:00:10.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The unwanted guest calls for a case.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.15,0:00:12.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.70,0:00:14.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A child with the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.45,0:00:16.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.24,0:01:45.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, we would like to get to Hotel Arimori.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.12,0:01:48.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, just go across, and head straight on the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.58,0:01:50.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.80,0:01:59.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad, I'm surprised you knew about a hotel all the way out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.34,0:02:03.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because this place is known for its great local beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.85,0:02:05.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alcohol was his goal again?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.56,0:02:06.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.65,0:02:10.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.56,0:02:11.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're finally here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.69,0:02:21.70,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,THE BLACK WINGS OF ICARUS
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.69,0:02:21.70,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,(PART ONE)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.66,0:02:27.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.66,0:02:29.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I made a reservation, under Mouri.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.75,0:02:35.88,Character Card,Sign,0,0,0,,Hotel Manager
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.75,0:02:35.88,Character Card,Sign,0,0,0,,Arimori Mitsuyuki (32)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.67,0:02:32.75,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Mouri Kogorou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}, I believe?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.75,0:02:33.79,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,We've been expecting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.50,0:02:35.88,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I am the manager, Arimori.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.42,0:02:38.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're looking forward to our stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.30,0:02:40.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please check-in on this card.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.76,0:02:44.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.85,0:02:47.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't I meet you two...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.10,0:02:52.23,Character Card,Sign,0,0,0,,Shimokasa Minaho (21)\NEmployee
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.10,0:02:52.23,Character Card,Sign,0,0,0,,Shimokasa Honami (21)\NEmployee
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.60,0:02:49.56,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,On that cursed mask case?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.77,0:02:52.23,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much for your help then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.06,0:02:54.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you two doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.23,0:02:56.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a request from a friend of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.07,0:03:00.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They've been excited about your arrival as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.16,0:03:05.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just hope there aren't any cursed objects here as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.95,0:03:09.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I made a reservation, under Shiromoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.46,0:03:11.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.50,0:03:14.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shiromoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.84,0:03:17.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You must be Shiromoto Hidehiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.05,0:03:19.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wasn't the reservation for two?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.13,0:03:20.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.47,0:03:24.89,Character Card,Sign,0,0,0,,Businessman
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.47,0:03:24.89,Character Card,Sign,0,0,0,,Shiromoto Hidehiko (46)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.97,0:03:22.26,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,My wife and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.89,0:03:24.85,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she'll be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.18,0:03:27.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't care what the producer's excuse is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.93,0:03:30.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this about me having to give up my part all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.39,0:03:32.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're headed this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.98,0:03:34.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't have to come anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.48,0:03:39.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't she...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.53,0:03:41.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That actress, Bizen Chizuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.11,0:03:42.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.49,0:03:45.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dear, what's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.58,0:03:50.87,Character Card,Sign,0,0,0,,Actress · Shiromoto's Wife
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.58,0:03:50.87,Character Card,Sign,0,0,0,,Bizen Chizuru (30)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.99,0:03:49.16,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I came because I was told this was a beautiful place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.16,0:03:50.87,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,It turns out, you've brought me to the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.71,0:03:53.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it's a nice and quiet place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.58,0:03:58.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To think I'll have to see your face and stay here for\Nthe next few days, it's getting on my nerves...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.00,0:04:00.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Front Manager, give me a different room from this person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.05,0:04:03.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, Miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.14,0:04:08.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please give the reserved suite to my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.47,0:04:09.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll take a different room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.43,0:04:11.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.10,0:04:14.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, take care of my things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.02,0:04:17.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeez, not even an elevator?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.07,0:04:22.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her image is different from TV and the movies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.03,0:04:26.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Minaho{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, Honami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.49,0:04:27.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Show them around.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.70,0:04:28.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.87,0:04:33.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.34,0:04:44.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}, would you like to rest at the restaurant?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.30,0:04:45.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Restaurant?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:48.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At this time, we can offer you cold herbal tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.10,0:04:51.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How great.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.27,0:04:53.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey Dad, let's go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.48,0:04:54.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.19,0:04:57.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Instead of herbal tea, I prefer...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.57,0:05:01.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's such a nice restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.74,0:05:03.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.32,0:05:06.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She is our chef.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.12,0:05:12.41,Character Card,Sign,0,0,0,,Hotel Arimori Chef
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.12,0:05:12.41,Character Card,Sign,0,0,0,,Simon Shinobu (27)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.70,0:05:09.87,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I'm Shimon Shinobu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.58,0:05:12.12,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Welcome to our restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.75,0:05:17.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This restaurant's layout and decorations\Nwere designed entirely by her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.33,0:05:19.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.38,0:05:28.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hope you will enjoy the delicious food made\Nfrom local ingredients in this relaxing environment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.01,0:05:30.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't wait until dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.64,0:05:33.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard something about a tasty local beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.48,0:05:36.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've prepared it, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.85,0:05:40.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinobu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, bring out some herbal tea for the guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.48,0:05:40.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.40,0:05:43.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'll take the local beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.23,0:05:45.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait until dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.62,0:05:55.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So great!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.29,0:05:59.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad, why don't you stop drinking\Nso much beer and eat some food?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.04,0:06:02.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The soup is really tasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.00,0:06:04.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've never had soup as bad as this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.26,0:06:07.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you really a chef?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.80,0:06:09.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chizuru, stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.39,0:06:10.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.84,0:06:15.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, but could you tell me how it does not suit your taste?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.18,0:06:18.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"How"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.19,0:06:21.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your customer is saying it's horrible, so\Nyou should at least lower your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.77,0:06:23.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.98,0:06:25.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll bring out another soup immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.53,0:06:28.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinobu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.70,0:06:29.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.57,0:06:32.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.74,0:06:36.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what she should have done from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.76,0:06:53.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard of you from my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.72,0:06:55.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're that renowned detective...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.93,0:06:57.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri Kogorou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, I believe?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.39,0:07:00.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm glad we have met.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.10,0:07:02.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm glad as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.27,0:07:08.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I always look forward to hearing stories of your latest exploits.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.53,0:07:16.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Chizuru's husband, Shiromoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.66,0:07:22.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've come here on vacation after finalizing\Nthe development plan for Vager Land.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.79,0:07:25.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-You're a businessman, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.00,0:07:29.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the rumors about the development were really true?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.67,0:07:35.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the plateau near by, there are\Nmany rare butterflies and plants.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.72,0:07:38.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How do you plan to ensure their safety?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.85,0:07:43.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm planning to meet with the locals\Nat the bottom of the mountain about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.73,0:07:45.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The locals? So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.27,0:07:48.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are always those people who talk\Nabout preserving nature everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.69,0:07:50.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all money, all money.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.90,0:07:52.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chizuru, how could you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.28,0:07:55.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, did I strike a nerve?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.91,0:07:58.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you want a divorce, I can separate from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.87,0:07:59.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.62,0:08:02.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder if you could afford my compensation?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.58,0:08:05.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chizuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.76,0:08:13.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chizuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, please just give up your part this once!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.84,0:08:17.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Manager, are you still talking about stupid things like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.51,0:08:19.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First of all, what's the reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.52,0:08:22.73,Character Card,Sign,0,0,0,,Drama Production Company President
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.52,0:08:22.73,Character Card,Sign,0,0,0,,Miyabe Kouta (35)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.97,0:08:22.73,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Chizuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, I really can't say here...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.31,0:08:24.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry, just say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.10,0:08:29.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Well, actually, the sponsors don't agree with\NChizuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} being... Maybe a younger actress...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.65,0:08:30.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.48,0:08:35.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They won't agree to funding us unless we use Reika{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r},\Nwho's at the top of her career from last year's performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.24,0:08:37.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Reika{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} is one of our actresses as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.82,0:08:40.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, if we don't do this movie, it'll\Nbe devastating to our company.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.12,0:08:43.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please understand, Chizuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.25,0:08:46.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.12,0:08:47.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with all your eyes!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.21,0:08:50.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're all probably thinking that everything would\Nbe better if I disappeared, aren't you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.76,0:08:53.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fine, I'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.92,0:08:55.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chizuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.30,0:08:59.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's troublesome...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.01,0:09:02.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, please don't let it bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.89,0:09:05.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, is this you, Arimori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.23,0:09:09.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, in this photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.15,0:09:11.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's you in the middle, Arimori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.78,0:09:13.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinobu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is the one on the right, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.19,0:09:15.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.15,0:09:19.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She and I are old hang gliding friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.16,0:09:21.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hang gliding?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.20,0:09:26.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A long time ago, we were able to hang glide from a nearby cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.04,0:09:30.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, it's impossible due to the land development.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.09,0:09:32.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.17,0:09:34.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I did it too when I was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.59,0:09:37.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who's the man standing next to Arimori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.05,0:09:41.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's my younger brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.76,0:09:44.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We flew together often back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.89,0:09:47.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been five years since we've flown, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.89,0:09:51.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The hang gliders are just stuffed\Nin the storage room on the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.07,0:09:56.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, let's go to the plateau tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.15,0:09:58.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's perfect for the photos you need for your homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.67,0:10:13.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle is snoring too loud for me to get any sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.05,0:10:17.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think I'll go buy some juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.93,0:10:26.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't reach it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.06,0:10:27.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Enough already!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.06,0:10:29.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.77,0:10:30.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That doesn't concern me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.87,0:10:47.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chizuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.46,0:10:49.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just what's with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.63,0:10:58.01,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,9:00 A.M.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.63,0:10:58.01,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,The Next Morning
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.26,0:11:06.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shiromoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.72,0:11:08.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How is Chizuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.85,0:11:11.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry about last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.06,0:11:13.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's usually what happens, so don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.61,0:11:15.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She'll probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.74,0:11:24.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um, Chizuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.24,0:11:27.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No, it's nothing at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.95,0:11:29.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey old lady, last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.54,0:11:33.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by "old lady"!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.63,0:11:35.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please don't let that bother you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.88,0:11:43.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just what are we gonna do!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.05,0:11:46.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right now, it's impossible to persuade her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.39,0:11:50.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you say we go fish until she cools down?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.81,0:11:55.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I start working tomorrow, so I've\Nbeen planning to fish all day today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.02,0:11:58.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you wish, I'll lend you my rod as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.61,0:12:01.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, in that case, I'd be glad to join you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.07,0:12:05.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad, let's go to the plateau.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.70,0:12:07.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You all can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.78,0:12:10.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I still have an important mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.08,0:12:10.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.95,0:12:15.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, I watch Okino Youko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}'s new promotional video.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.58,0:12:19.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, I watch the broadcast of her concert from last month.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.09,0:12:25.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lastly, I will watch a re-run of her drama special!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.34,0:12:27.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad, what did you come all the way here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.05,0:12:31.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The re-run of her drama is only playing in this area...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.18,0:12:34.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You came all the way out here to watch that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.90,0:12:38.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you don't mind, I'd like to take you to the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.61,0:12:41.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That would be great!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.78,0:12:42.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.82,0:12:45.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you like to go with them, Shinobu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.32,0:12:48.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll watch the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.24,0:12:52.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, I still have to prepare everyone's meals...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.50,0:12:56.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, just make us bentos for lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.04,0:13:00.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We will be leaving as well, so we don't mind bentos.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.63,0:13:03.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I still have to prepare dinner...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.76,0:13:07.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, how about we barbecue in the yard for dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.72,0:13:09.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That will be easy to prepare, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.18,0:13:12.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My wife was so rude to you last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.60,0:13:15.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To make up for it, please go stretch your wings today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.94,0:13:19.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's only setting it up, we'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.11,0:13:22.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There aren't any new guests arriving today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.57,0:13:25.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you go along with their suggestion?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:27.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go ahead, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.41,0:13:30.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, I'll do as you've suggested.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.33,0:13:34.54,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,It should be only about 15 minutes to the lake by car.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.16,0:13:37.58,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,The Departure
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.16,0:13:37.58,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,10:00 A.M.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.96,0:13:35.87,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Do you know the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.33,0:13:37.58,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.33,0:13:41.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That spot is best right after the sun sets.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.17,0:13:43.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, I guess we'll be fishing through nightfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.38,0:13:47.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have a safe trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.10,0:13:55.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll go check the locks and come in the micro-bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.73,0:13:57.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll catch up, so go ahead without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.94,0:13:59.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.44,0:13:59.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.65,0:14:10.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chizuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} would feel better if she came\Noutside instead of staying in her room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.37,0:14:14.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mission #1!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.37,0:14:20.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Time to watch Youko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}'s new PV and master the lyrics!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.88,0:14:23.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Youko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.25,0:14:23.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.71,0:14:25.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.55,0:14:28.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll leave the master key here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.76,0:14:29.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please take good care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:31.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.44,0:14:41.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeez, Dad is hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.61,0:14:42.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Arimori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} still hasn't come?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.15,0:14:46.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, there he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.70,0:14:56.83,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Arrival at the Plateau
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.70,0:14:56.83,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,10:50 A.M.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.58,0:15:01.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This cool wind feels great.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.89,0:15:19.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.60,0:15:20.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.00,0:15:42.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the sky really is this blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.83,0:15:44.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I never noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.00,0:15:47.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It feels like if I had wings...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.42,0:15:49.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I could fly to the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.84,0:15:52.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That sounds like something Icarus would say.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.09,0:15:54.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Icarus?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.05,0:15:55.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Greek Mythology.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.89,0:15:58.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Icarus, who received wings...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.02,0:16:02.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Forgot his father's warning that he shouldn't fly too high...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.02,0:16:04.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And flew higher and higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.61,0:16:07.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He believed he could fly to the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.82,0:16:09.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.57,0:16:13.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Icarus' wings couldn't bear the heat\Nwhen he got too close to the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.12,0:16:19.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After his wings burned, Icarus fell\Nfrom the sky right to the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.29,0:16:24.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a sad story.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.55,0:16:29.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a cute butterfly!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.05,0:16:33.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's a Miyama white butterfly that only exists around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.56,0:16:43.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The butterfly...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.06,0:16:50.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This butterfly can't survive unless the water is clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.07,0:16:58.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Youko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.45,0:16:59.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Youko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.83,0:17:02.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Youko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.87,0:17:07.67,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Hotel Lobby
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.87,0:17:07.67,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,12:30 P.M.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.38,0:17:10.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I forgot my bento.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.76,0:17:14.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is Chizuru still in her room?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.92,0:17:15.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.76,0:17:17.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She has not come down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.09,0:17:20.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll go see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.39,0:17:29.90,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Lakeside
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.39,0:17:29.90,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,1:00 P.M.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.36,0:17:39.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Chizuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}'s in a better mood yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.12,0:17:48.37,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Hotel Lobby
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.12,0:17:48.37,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,1:30 P.M.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.83,0:17:48.63,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,How was your wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.63,0:17:49.21,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.96,0:17:52.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems as if she's still asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.50,0:17:54.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knocked, but there was no answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.38,0:17:58.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As someone who also has a tough wife, I know how difficult it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.43,0:18:00.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.06,0:18:03.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll be going back to my fishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.64,0:18:05.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have a good trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.02,0:18:12.98,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Plateau
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.02,0:18:12.98,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,1:50 P.M.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.24,0:18:18.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Out of bounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.03,0:18:19.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.61,0:18:21.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's have lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.24,0:18:23.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's already this late?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.12,0:18:24.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll go get the bentos.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.21,0:18:35.34,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Lake
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.21,0:18:35.34,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,2:15 P.M.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.29,0:18:34.59,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,This is a big one!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.42,0:18:38.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've got tons today!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.80,0:18:39.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.76,0:18:49.89,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Hotel Lobby
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.76,0:18:49.89,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,2:25 P.M.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.10,0:18:49.89,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Youko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, you can't go that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.90,0:18:55.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.03,0:18:57.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It really is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.82,0:19:00.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The sunset from here is always wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.41,0:19:05.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, the bright area at the bottom there is Hotel Arimori.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.83,0:19:08.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's that far?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.04,0:19:11.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.83,0:19:12.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.96,0:19:16.75,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Starting Down the Mountain
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.96,0:19:16.75,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,6:05 P.M.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.14,0:19:23.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.26,0:19:26.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The engine doesn't seem so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.47,0:19:28.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go back ahead of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.52,0:19:30.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.86,0:19:40.57,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Hotel
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.86,0:19:40.57,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,7:00 P.M.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.94,0:19:40.11,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,We're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.95,0:19:43.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeez, you should have come with us, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.03,0:19:45.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The sunset was wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.24,0:19:47.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, and there was this rare butterfly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.37,0:19:51.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's said that it doesn't get close to humans, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.12,0:19:53.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It landed right on Arimori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s shoulder!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.96,0:19:55.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I get it, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.38,0:19:57.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.38,0:19:59.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've got tons!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.42,0:20:01.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.30,0:20:03.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's Chizuru up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.97,0:20:06.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, she never came down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.26,0:20:07.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Never?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.64,0:20:10.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeez, that troublesome woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.64,0:20:14.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, may I borrow the master key?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.77,0:20:16.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.69,0:20:18.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.45,0:20:23.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, today's catch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.74,0:20:24.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll leave the rest to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.45,0:20:26.16,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Hello? This is Hotel Arimori.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.70,0:20:28.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Arimori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.49,0:20:30.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The car won't start.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.12,0:20:32.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry to ask, but could you come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.41,0:20:33.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.67,0:20:40.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You might need some help, so I'll come too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.17,0:20:42.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry to trouble you, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.27,0:20:56.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, there's something wrong with Chizuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.23,0:21:01.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I opened the door with the key, but the door guard is on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.53,0:21:03.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter how much I call, there's no answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.95,0:21:05.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.24,0:21:13.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chizuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}! Chizuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.91,0:21:15.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's break the door down.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.37,0:21:16.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.17,0:21:27.76,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Body Discovered
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.17,0:21:27.76,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,7:20 P.M.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.47,0:21:30.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chizuru!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.31,0:21:31.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chizuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.35,0:21:39.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.19,0:21:39.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How's Chizuru?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.90,0:21:42.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to say, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.28,0:21:45.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It appears it's been some time since she passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.74,0:21:52.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.37,0:21:58.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The door guard lock...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.08,0:22:00.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These marks are...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.17,0:22:03.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.63,0:22:07.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.22,0:22:10.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chizuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.80,0:22:12.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chizuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} didn't commit suicide!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.68,0:22:16.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was murdered!
Comment: 0,0:22:20.61,0:22:26.69,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,THE BLACK WINGS OF ICARUS
Comment: 0,0:22:20.61,0:22:26.69,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,(PART TWO)
Comment: 0,0:22:26.99,0:22:30.16,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Plateau
Comment: 0,0:22:26.99,0:22:30.16,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,8:00 P.M.
Comment: 0,0:22:32.20,0:22:33.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Arimori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Comment: 0,0:22:33.45,0:22:34.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Arimori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Comment: 0,0:22:35.58,0:22:36.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where is he?
Comment: 0,0:22:36.33,0:22:37.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Arimori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Comment: 0,0:22:37.37,0:22:38.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm over here!
Comment: 0,0:22:40.08,0:22:43.00,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Hotel Manager
Comment: 0,0:22:40.08,0:22:43.00,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Arimori Mitsuyuki (32)
Comment: 0,0:22:40.58,0:22:43.00,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,The stars were so beautiful that I got lost in them.
Comment: 0,0:22:43.42,0:22:45.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeez, Arimori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Comment: 0,0:22:49.26,0:22:50.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Comment: 0,0:22:50.34,0:22:51.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Minaho{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Comment: 0,0:22:53.10,0:22:53.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What'd you say!?
Comment: 0,0:22:55.14,0:22:55.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Comment: 0,0:22:55.81,0:22:56.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be there right away!
Comment: 0,0:22:56.97,0:22:58.85,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Simon Shinobu (27)\NHotel Arimori Chef
Comment: 0,0:22:57.68,0:22:58.48,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Comment: 0,0:22:59.60,0:23:01.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like Chizuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} passed away...
Comment: 0,0:23:02.40,0:23:04.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's leave the bus here and get back to the hotel.
Comment: 0,0:23:05.90,0:23:06.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right!
Comment: 0,0:23:07.07,0:23:09.86,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Hotel
Comment: 0,0:23:07.07,0:23:09.86,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,8:20 P.M.
Comment: 0,0:23:08.61,0:23:09.86,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,The deceased is...
Comment: 0,0:23:09.86,0:23:12.32,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,The actress, Bizen Chizuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, age thirty.
Comment: 0,0:23:12.87,0:23:17.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was lodging at this hotel with her\Nhusband, Shiromoto Hidehiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Comment: 0,0:23:18.75,0:23:20.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the estimated time of death?
Comment: 0,0:23:21.17,0:23:25.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The estimated time of death is between 1:30 P.M. and 2:30 P.M.
Comment: 0,0:23:26.00,0:23:29.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The cause of death is likely to be\Nsuffocation from a blocked airway.
Comment: 0,0:23:29.59,0:23:34.97,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Mito Kouichi (33)\NNagano Province Detective
Comment: 0,0:23:29.84,0:23:34.93,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,At the time that you discovered the body,\Nis it true that the door guard was active?
Comment: 0,0:23:35.56,0:23:39.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's why I had no choice but to\Nbreak the door open with a tackle.
Comment: 0,0:23:40.64,0:23:43.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The windows were locked from the inside as well.
Comment: 0,0:23:43.65,0:23:45.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no mistake in saying it was a suicide.
Comment: 0,0:23:45.69,0:23:49.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Bizen Chizuru was a famous actress...
Comment: 0,0:23:50.11,0:23:52.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was there any reason for her to commit suicide?
Comment: 0,0:23:53.16,0:23:56.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, last night there was some trouble.
Comment: 0,0:23:56.41,0:23:57.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Trouble?
Comment: 0,0:23:57.79,0:24:01.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was forced to give up a part in\Na movie that was promised to her.
Comment: 0,0:24:01.91,0:24:04.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seemed to come as a great shock to her.
Comment: 0,0:24:05.88,0:24:06.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Comment: 0,0:24:07.50,0:24:08.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Comment: 0,0:24:09.42,0:24:10.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Boy, you can't go in!
Comment: 0,0:24:11.59,0:24:12.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Comment: 0,0:24:13.22,0:24:15.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That brat again...
Comment: 0,0:24:16.60,0:24:18.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you running around again?
Comment: 0,0:24:18.68,0:24:21.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because there are some strange marks over here...
Comment: 0,0:24:21.98,0:24:22.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Marks?
Comment: 0,0:24:23.23,0:24:25.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is where the door guard's lock was.
Comment: 0,0:24:26.15,0:24:28.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are strange marks on the lock as well.
Comment: 0,0:24:28.90,0:24:34.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These could be made after someone from the\Noutside created this locked room scenario.
Comment: 0,0:24:35.87,0:24:36.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Comment: 0,0:24:37.28,0:24:40.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Meaning, after the culprit locked the windows...
Comment: 0,0:24:41.12,0:24:45.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They used a screwdriver and removed\Nthe door guard from the wall.
Comment: 0,0:24:45.83,0:24:50.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, they placed the door guard back\Non as they stepped into the hall...
Comment: 0,0:24:50.55,0:24:53.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, from the opening in the door, rescrewed the lock in.
Comment: 0,0:24:53.72,0:24:59.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, it's difficult to do such a demanding task in a\Nsmall area, so it's no surprise that the marks are there.
Comment: 0,0:25:00.39,0:25:04.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The reason it was displaced with just one tackle...
Comment: 0,0:25:04.52,0:25:06.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Must be because the screws weren't completely in.
Comment: 0,0:25:08.02,0:25:13.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Chizuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} moved this table from\Nthe window and used it as a stool, right?
Comment: 0,0:25:13.19,0:25:14.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Comment: 0,0:25:14.99,0:25:15.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then...
Comment: 0,0:25:16.86,0:25:19.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop bothering the crime scene people!
Comment: 0,0:25:19.53,0:25:21.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, are there prints on toes?
Comment: 0,0:25:23.75,0:25:24.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course there is!
Comment: 0,0:25:24.83,0:25:25.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at your own foot...
Comment: 0,0:25:26.17,0:25:27.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, wait a second!
Comment: 0,0:25:27.63,0:25:29.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chizuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s feet were bear!
Comment: 0,0:25:31.42,0:25:34.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Were there any such prints on the table?
Comment: 0,0:25:35.68,0:25:36.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There weren't!
Comment: 0,0:25:37.09,0:25:38.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What now?
Comment: 0,0:25:38.68,0:25:39.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-That means...
Comment: 0,0:25:40.14,0:25:42.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone carried Chizuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} here and hung her.
Comment: 0,0:25:43.56,0:25:45.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means it wasn't suicide, but murder.
Comment: 0,0:25:46.64,0:25:50.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Last night, Chizuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} had a conflict\Nwith someone in the restaurant...
Comment: 0,0:25:50.98,0:25:53.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn, if only I had saw who it was then...
Comment: 0,0:25:55.70,0:25:57.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are there any other clues?
Comment: 0,0:26:00.03,0:26:00.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Comment: 0,0:26:01.24,0:26:03.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's like a white powder...
Comment: 0,0:26:05.16,0:26:07.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This room is so warm...
Comment: 0,0:26:08.96,0:26:09.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Air conditioning!?
Comment: 0,0:26:10.21,0:26:12.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that I think about it, it was off when we found the body!
Comment: 0,0:26:13.71,0:26:15.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did the culprit go to the trouble of turning it off?
Comment: 0,0:26:16.13,0:26:16.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or maybe...
Comment: 0,0:26:22.81,0:26:25.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Regarding the death of Bizen Chizuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Comment: 0,0:26:26.18,0:26:28.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I would like to ask all of you some questions.
Comment: 0,0:26:28.73,0:26:30.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You first, Shiromoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Comment: 0,0:26:32.11,0:26:35.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm told you were arguing with Chizuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} over divorce issues?
Comment: 0,0:26:35.61,0:26:40.24,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Businessman
Comment: 0,0:26:35.61,0:26:40.24,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Shiromoto Hidehiko (46)
Comment: 0,0:26:35.90,0:26:40.24,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Yes, her company loans were huge, and...
Comment: 0,0:26:42.07,0:26:43.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're next, Miyabe{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Comment: 0,0:26:43.53,0:26:47.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm told you dropped her as the lead in a movie recently?
Comment: 0,0:26:47.41,0:26:51.75,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Drama Production Company President
Comment: 0,0:26:47.41,0:26:51.75,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Miyabe Kouta (35)
Comment: 0,0:26:47.71,0:26:49.83,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,It wasn't my call at all.
Comment: 0,0:26:49.83,0:26:51.75,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,The sponsors were the ones who wanted her gone.
Comment: 0,0:26:52.21,0:26:53.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Comment: 0,0:26:53.92,0:26:55.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I would like all of you to answer this.
Comment: 0,0:26:56.67,0:27:01.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The estimated time of death is between 1:30 P.M. and 2:30 P.M.
Comment: 0,0:27:01.93,0:27:04.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please tell me what you all were doing at that time.
Comment: 0,0:27:05.39,0:27:07.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Comment: 0,0:27:07.06,0:27:09.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It sounds like you're looking for alibis...
Comment: 0,0:27:09.10,0:27:10.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Was Chizuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}...
Comment: 0,0:27:11.35,0:27:13.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From what we found at the scene...
Comment: 0,0:27:13.23,0:27:15.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's very likely that it was a murder.
Comment: 0,0:27:16.23,0:27:17.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No way...
Comment: 0,0:27:17.82,0:27:22.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shiromoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and Miyabe{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, you two\Nwent to a local lake to fish, did you not?
Comment: 0,0:27:23.24,0:27:25.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right —\hThat's right.
Comment: 0,0:27:25.58,0:27:30.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From when we left at 10:00 AM and returned\Nto the hotel at 7:00 PM, I was at the lake.
Comment: 0,0:27:30.21,0:27:30.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you, too, Shiromoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Comment: 0,0:27:31.37,0:27:33.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I forgot my bento.
Comment: 0,0:27:34.84,0:27:37.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I came back to the hotel at 12:30 P.M.
Comment: 0,0:27:37.63,0:27:41.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I ate lunch in the lobby with Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and left at 1:30 P.M.
Comment: 0,0:27:42.43,0:27:44.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, did you see Chizuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} at that time?
Comment: 0,0:27:45.43,0:27:49.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I went to her room to check on her...
Comment: 0,0:27:49.39,0:27:52.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But when she didn't answer my knocking, I returned to the lobby.
Comment: 0,0:27:53.90,0:27:56.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When Shiromoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} went back to the hotel...
Comment: 0,0:27:56.52,0:27:58.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Weren't you completely alone, Miyabe{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Comment: 0,0:27:59.57,0:28:01.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-That's true, but...
Comment: 0,0:28:01.61,0:28:04.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was eating my bento on the lakeside the whole time.
Comment: 0,0:28:05.49,0:28:07.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you two, Arimori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and Shinobu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Comment: 0,0:28:07.49,0:28:12.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We went to the plateau on top of the\Nmountain with Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Comment: 0,0:28:12.21,0:28:15.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We left immediately after Shiromoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} did...
Comment: 0,0:28:16.29,0:28:18.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And arrived there at around 11:00 A.M.
Comment: 0,0:28:18.92,0:28:22.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were there the entire time and\Ncame down the mountain at 6:00 P.M.
Comment: 0,0:28:24.14,0:28:26.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was around 7:00 P.M. when we made it back to the hotel.
Comment: 0,0:28:26.85,0:28:29.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I'm told that Arimori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} remained alone at the plateau?
Comment: 0,0:28:29.85,0:28:32.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The micro-bus's engine wasn't doing well, so...
Comment: 0,0:28:33.52,0:28:36.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And Arimori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was at the field when you went to pick him up?
Comment: 0,0:28:36.81,0:28:37.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Comment: 0,0:28:38.32,0:28:41.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no mistake, as I was with her.
Comment: 0,0:28:41.99,0:28:43.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And Minaho{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and Honami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Comment: 0,0:28:44.20,0:28:46.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,During the morning, we were cleaning the hotel.
Comment: 0,0:28:47.53,0:28:48.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After Shiromoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r} came back...
Comment: 0,0:28:49.79,0:28:53.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We brought out tea to him and Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r} for their lunch.
Comment: 0,0:28:53.58,0:28:56.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Afterwards, we had lunch in the office.
Comment: 0,0:28:56.54,0:28:59.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At 1:30 P.M., after walking Shiromoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r} to the door...
Comment: 0,0:29:00.05,0:29:02.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We watched television with Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r} until 4:00 P.M.
Comment: 0,0:29:03.47,0:29:08.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Afterwards, until everyone returned, we were preparing dinner.
Comment: 0,0:29:09.72,0:29:11.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How was Chizuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s room when you were cleaning?
Comment: 0,0:29:12.48,0:29:16.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were told by the manager to leave it alone...
Comment: 0,0:29:16.02,0:29:17.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So we never went near it.
Comment: 0,0:29:18.40,0:29:20.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, you were always here?
Comment: 0,0:29:20.65,0:29:23.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I was watching TV in the lobby all day.
Comment: 0,0:29:24.24,0:29:27.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excluding when Shiromoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Nwent to check on her at 12:30 P.M...
Comment: 0,0:29:28.45,0:29:30.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No one used the staircase in the lobby.
Comment: 0,0:29:31.24,0:29:35.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means the culprit must have entered the\Nhotel through one of the emergency exits.
Comment: 0,0:29:35.96,0:29:37.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are the emergency exits like?
Comment: 0,0:29:38.54,0:29:40.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's one at the end of every floor's hall.
Comment: 0,0:29:41.67,0:29:45.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The doors auto-lock, but can be opened freely from inside.
Comment: 0,0:29:46.09,0:29:49.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't open it from outside without the master key.
Comment: 0,0:29:49.76,0:29:53.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-That means the culprit is someone from the hotel!
Comment: 0,0:29:53.64,0:29:56.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I had the master key all day.
Comment: 0,0:29:57.81,0:30:00.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The person must have made a spare beforehand.
Comment: 0,0:30:00.36,0:30:03.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's so, the culprits must be those two!
Comment: 0,0:30:03.82,0:30:05.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We didn't do anything!
Comment: 0,0:30:06.45,0:30:11.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From 1:30 P.M. until 4:00 P.M., they were watching TV with me.
Comment: 0,0:30:11.37,0:30:13.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-Then, you three must have worked in a group!
Comment: 0,0:30:13.91,0:30:15.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!? That's stupid!
Comment: 0,0:30:15.96,0:30:17.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,E-Either way...
Comment: 0,0:30:17.54,0:30:20.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since I didn't have the master key, I can't be the culprit.
Comment: 0,0:30:20.96,0:30:23.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, even without the master key...
Comment: 0,0:30:23.00,0:30:24.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's still a way to get in from the emergency exit.
Comment: 0,0:30:25.67,0:30:27.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, even without the master key...
Comment: 0,0:30:27.93,0:30:30.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's still a way to get in from the emergency exit.
Comment: 0,0:30:33.10,0:30:34.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For example, Shiromoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Comment: 0,0:30:35.10,0:30:37.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At 12:30 P.M., when you went to check on Chizuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Comment: 0,0:30:38.48,0:30:40.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You could have opened the emergency exit from inside...
Comment: 0,0:30:41.36,0:30:44.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then placed a small rock to ensure\Nthe door wouldn't completely close.
Comment: 0,0:30:45.23,0:30:49.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, at 1:30 P.M., you could have\Npretended to be going back to the lake...
Comment: 0,0:30:49.07,0:30:52.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you were really going back to the hotel\Nthrough the emergency exit to murder Chizuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Comment: 0,0:30:53.12,0:30:54.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No way...
Comment: 0,0:30:55.20,0:30:56.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This guy's pretty good.
Comment: 0,0:30:57.50,0:31:01.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Miyabe{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, if he were working with you, it's\Npossible for you to have committed the crime.
Comment: 0,0:31:01.79,0:31:03.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you saying, Detective?
Comment: 0,0:31:04.25,0:31:07.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By hiding in Shiromoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s car, you\Ncould have returned to the hotel.
Comment: 0,0:31:07.38,0:31:10.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, you could enter from the emergency\Nexit that Shiromoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} opened and...
Comment: 0,0:31:11.30,0:31:12.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's enough already!
Comment: 0,0:31:13.01,0:31:15.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're talking to them like they're the culprits!
Comment: 0,0:31:16.64,0:31:18.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm just saying...
Comment: 0,0:31:18.77,0:31:20.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about you all?
Comment: 0,0:31:21.10,0:31:22.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Comment: 0,0:31:22.73,0:31:26.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You guys could have had a spare of the master key.
Comment: 0,0:31:26.82,0:31:28.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You could secretly come down...
Comment: 0,0:31:28.61,0:31:30.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop saying such stupid things!
Comment: 0,0:31:31.03,0:31:33.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In order to return to the hotel from the plateau or the lake...
Comment: 0,0:31:35.08,0:31:38.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You would have to cross the bridge that's under construction.
Comment: 0,0:31:39.12,0:31:41.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Earlier, when we checked with the workers...
Comment: 0,0:31:41.96,0:31:46.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They said the only car that went back to the\Nhotel around noon was Shiromoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s car.
Comment: 0,0:31:47.50,0:31:49.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means the only ones who could have done it are...
Comment: 0,0:31:50.26,0:31:50.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shiromoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Comment: 0,0:31:51.93,0:31:52.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Miyabe{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Comment: 0,0:31:53.55,0:31:54.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Minaho{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, Honami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Comment: 0,0:31:56.35,0:31:57.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Comment: 0,0:31:58.31,0:31:59.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me too!?
Comment: 0,0:32:00.35,0:32:02.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's exactly as Detective Mito says...
Comment: 0,0:32:02.77,0:32:04.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But something doesn't seem right.
Comment: 0,0:32:05.31,0:32:06.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Specifically...
Comment: 0,0:32:07.52,0:32:08.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The air conditioning that had stopped...
Comment: 0,0:32:10.03,0:32:12.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that white powder on Chizuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s skirt...
Comment: 0,0:32:14.03,0:32:15.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Comment: 0,0:32:16.95,0:32:17.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!
Comment: 0,0:32:17.99,0:32:18.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Comment: 0,0:32:25.25,0:32:27.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is almost like a runway...
Comment: 0,0:32:33.68,0:32:34.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's...
Comment: 0,0:32:35.14,0:32:36.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A rope mark, isn't it?
Comment: 0,0:32:52.53,0:32:53.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Officer!
Comment: 0,0:32:54.91,0:32:57.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle Mouri told me to ask...
Comment: 0,0:32:58.99,0:32:59.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At any rate...
Comment: 0,0:32:59.91,0:33:00.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shiromoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Comment: 0,0:33:01.00,0:33:01.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Miyabe{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Comment: 0,0:33:02.04,0:33:02.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Minaho{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Comment: 0,0:33:02.91,0:33:03.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Honami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Comment: 0,0:33:04.04,0:33:04.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Comment: 0,0:33:04.92,0:33:06.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I would like to ask you more intimate questions at the station.
Comment: 0,0:33:06.58,0:33:09.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey you, do you know who I am?
Comment: 0,0:33:14.55,0:33:15.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, what's wrong?
Comment: 0,0:33:17.30,0:33:18.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please wait.
Comment: 0,0:33:18.26,0:33:20.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the beginning of "Sleeping Kogorou."
Comment: 0,0:33:22.89,0:33:23.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Comment: 0,0:33:24.48,0:33:25.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the rumored...
Comment: 0,0:33:25.69,0:33:28.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please leave the rest to me.
Comment: 0,0:33:28.23,0:33:30.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means, you know who the culprit is?
Comment: 0,0:33:30.65,0:33:31.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Comment: 0,0:33:31.82,0:33:34.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know who the culprit is and the trick they used.
Comment: 0,0:33:35.45,0:33:36.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Trick?
Comment: 0,0:33:36.66,0:33:38.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit has wings.
Comment: 0,0:33:39.58,0:33:43.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They are what make this seemingly impossible crime possible...
Comment: 0,0:33:43.83,0:33:45.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those magical wings.
Comment: 0,0:33:46.12,0:33:46.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right...
Comment: 0,0:33:46.96,0:33:47.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit...
Comment: 0,0:33:48.46,0:33:49.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is you!
Comment: 0,0:33:53.76,0:33:54.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right...
Comment: 0,0:33:54.67,0:33:55.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit is you...
Comment: 0,0:33:56.38,0:33:57.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Arimori Mitsuyuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Comment: 0,0:34:02.89,0:34:04.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What are you saying?
Comment: 0,0:34:05.48,0:34:08.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was at the plateau with Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} the entire time.
Comment: 0,0:34:08.98,0:34:10.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Comment: 0,0:34:10.02,0:34:12.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Arimori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} cannot be the culprit.
Comment: 0,0:34:13.23,0:34:15.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't I just tell you?
Comment: 0,0:34:15.15,0:34:17.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Arimori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} had a pair of magical wings.
Comment: 0,0:34:18.24,0:34:20.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These "magical wings," what are they?
Comment: 0,0:34:27.08,0:34:28.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Comment: 0,0:34:28.58,0:34:31.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those are the magical wings.
Comment: 0,0:34:33.63,0:34:35.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We found it in the storage room on the roof.
Comment: 0,0:34:38.05,0:34:39.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a hang glider.
Comment: 0,0:34:39.34,0:34:40.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Comment: 0,0:34:40.34,0:34:47.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aside from this, there was a rope mark up\Nthere left just above the victim's room.
Comment: 0,0:34:48.27,0:34:49.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!
Comment: 0,0:34:49.69,0:34:51.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Arimori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} used that hang glider...
Comment: 0,0:34:52.48,0:34:55.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To fly from the plateau and land on the roof.
Comment: 0,0:34:56.65,0:34:59.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He used a rope to descend to the veranda outside her room.
Comment: 0,0:34:59.45,0:35:00.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And after he was done...
Comment: 0,0:35:00.86,0:35:03.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He flew right back using the hang glider.
Comment: 0,0:35:05.54,0:35:07.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What you've said is impossible.
Comment: 0,0:35:08.08,0:35:12.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only time I wasn't with the others was when I got the\Nbentos from the car, which only took four or five minutes.
Comment: 0,0:35:13.09,0:35:16.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It takes at least fifteen minutes to even set up a hang glider.
Comment: 0,0:35:17.05,0:35:19.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And about him returning to the hotel...
Comment: 0,0:35:19.68,0:35:22.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Judging from the wind direction and\Nthe incline, it's likely not possible.
Comment: 0,0:35:23.43,0:35:24.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Comment: 0,0:35:24.35,0:35:26.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's exactly as you all have said.
Comment: 0,0:35:27.10,0:35:28.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Comment: 0,0:35:28.10,0:35:32.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it was only to strangle Chizuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r},\Nit can be done in four or five minutes...
Comment: 0,0:35:32.52,0:35:34.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If she was nearby.
Comment: 0,0:35:35.73,0:35:37.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Comment: 0,0:35:37.03,0:35:38.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chizuru was at the hotel...
Comment: 0,0:35:38.65,0:35:39.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!
Comment: 0,0:35:39.90,0:35:41.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the micro-bus, isn't it?
Comment: 0,0:35:41.24,0:35:42.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Comment: 0,0:35:42.99,0:35:49.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, he separated from Shinobu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and the others during\Nthe departure by saying he was going to check the locks.
Comment: 0,0:35:49.62,0:35:51.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He then went to Chizuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s room...
Comment: 0,0:35:51.87,0:35:54.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And knocked her out with a stun-gun or something similar.
Comment: 0,0:35:54.42,0:35:59.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After putting her and the hang glider in\Nthe micro-bus, he went on to the plateau.
Comment: 0,0:35:59.84,0:36:00.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Mito...
Comment: 0,0:36:00.88,0:36:05.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you analyzed the scene, did you\Nrealize that the air conditioning was off?
Comment: 0,0:36:05.72,0:36:06.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Comment: 0,0:36:06.81,0:36:11.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means Chizuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} wasn't in the room after noon, right?
Comment: 0,0:36:11.77,0:36:13.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's exactly it.
Comment: 0,0:36:13.48,0:36:14.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, around 2:00 PM...
Comment: 0,0:36:15.61,0:36:19.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Arimori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} seperated from the others to get the bentos.
Comment: 0,0:36:20.61,0:36:23.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He returned to the micro-bus and the unconscious Chizuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Comment: 0,0:36:24.32,0:36:26.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And hung her with the rope.
Comment: 0,0:36:27.16,0:36:31.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Later, he claimed something was wrong with\Nthe engine so he could stay at the plateau.
Comment: 0,0:36:32.41,0:36:38.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, he set up the hang glider and flew\Nfrom the plateau with Chizuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} in tow.
Comment: 0,0:36:40.59,0:36:47.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since the roof of the hotel was lit up fairly\Nwell, I doubt he could have lost his way.
Comment: 0,0:36:47.60,0:36:56.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After landing on the roof, he descended via rope to the\Nveranda outside her room, and then hung the body inside.
Comment: 0,0:36:57.56,0:37:03.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Afterwards, you set up the door guard\Nand left the hotel via the emergency exit.
Comment: 0,0:37:04.11,0:37:05.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's foolish.
Comment: 0,0:37:05.41,0:37:08.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did I return to the plateau from there?
Comment: 0,0:37:08.37,0:37:09.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Comment: 0,0:37:09.33,0:37:12.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and I went back, Arimori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was there!
Comment: 0,0:37:13.66,0:37:15.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could he have used a bike?
Comment: 0,0:37:15.62,0:37:17.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The workers on the bridge would have seen him then.
Comment: 0,0:37:18.25,0:37:24.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's impossible to fly back with a hang glider at such\Na low angle as this to the top of the mountain.
Comment: 0,0:37:24.72,0:37:28.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I said Arimori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} used magic.
Comment: 0,0:37:28.64,0:37:32.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Magic that let him get back to the\Nplateau without anyone seeing him.
Comment: 0,0:37:32.52,0:37:34.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Again with things no one can understand...
Comment: 0,0:37:34.89,0:37:38.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The seed of his magic is Shinobu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s car.
Comment: 0,0:37:38.86,0:37:43.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the time Arimori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} called you on his cell phone...
Comment: 0,0:37:44.61,0:37:47.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was already in your car's trunk.
Comment: 0,0:37:47.95,0:37:48.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Comment: 0,0:37:49.20,0:37:53.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Arimori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} used Shinobu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} as\Nhis transport without her knowing.
Comment: 0,0:37:54.37,0:37:55.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once the car reached the plateau...
Comment: 0,0:37:56.92,0:37:59.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He waited for Ran and Shinobu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} to move away from the car...
Comment: 0,0:38:00.34,0:38:01.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then left the trunk.
Comment: 0,0:38:01.80,0:38:05.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, acting as if he'd been there all\Nalong, he appeared in front of them.
Comment: 0,0:38:07.47,0:38:08.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A-Arimori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Comment: 0,0:38:08.97,0:38:11.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-Those are all just theories!
Comment: 0,0:38:11.85,0:38:13.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you have some real proof?
Comment: 0,0:38:15.43,0:38:15.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Comment: 0,0:38:17.10,0:38:17.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Comment: 0,0:38:19.44,0:38:20.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Comment: 0,0:38:20.98,0:38:23.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, we've heard from the autopsy unit.
Comment: 0,0:38:23.69,0:38:27.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The white powder on the victim's skirt is\Nthe scale of a Miyama white butterfly.
Comment: 0,0:38:29.24,0:38:30.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And now you see...
Comment: 0,0:38:31.33,0:38:34.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the skirt of Chizuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, who was\Nsupposedly always at the hotel...
Comment: 0,0:38:34.66,0:38:40.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Were traces of a Miyama white butterfly\Nthat only exists on top of the mountain.
Comment: 0,0:38:41.42,0:38:42.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As Ran told me...
Comment: 0,0:38:43.30,0:38:47.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A butterfly landed on Arimori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s shoulder and died, didn't it?
Comment: 0,0:38:48.38,0:38:50.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That must be when its scale got on his shirt.
Comment: 0,0:38:51.26,0:38:53.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And when he put Chizuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} over\Nhis shoulder without noticing it...
Comment: 0,0:38:53.97,0:38:56.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The scale got on her skirt as well.
Comment: 0,0:38:57.39,0:38:59.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why, to Chizuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Comment: 0,0:39:01.48,0:39:02.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Revenge...
Comment: 0,0:39:03.23,0:39:04.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For my young brother.
Comment: 0,0:39:05.57,0:39:06.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Revenge?
Comment: 0,0:39:06.69,0:39:13.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Teruhiko was still at Tokyo University when he met\Nher, who was just beginning as an actress then.
Comment: 0,0:39:15.08,0:39:18.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To my younger brother, she became more and more to him.
Comment: 0,0:39:19.79,0:39:21.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But to Chizuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Comment: 0,0:39:21.25,0:39:22.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was just fun love.
Comment: 0,0:39:22.79,0:39:23.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Comment: 0,0:39:23.96,0:39:25.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From the start, she only wanted him for his money.
Comment: 0,0:39:27.09,0:39:28.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It cost him a lot to keep her around.
Comment: 0,0:39:30.34,0:39:33.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, as she became wealthier and\Nwealthier from her drama appearance...
Comment: 0,0:39:34.60,0:39:36.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She began to move away from Teruhiko.
Comment: 0,0:39:39.39,0:39:44.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To keep Chizuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s heart, Teruhiko began\Nto spend more and more money.
Comment: 0,0:39:45.86,0:39:50.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He even sold the hotel, which was obtained\Nfrom our father's will, without telling me...
Comment: 0,0:39:51.70,0:39:54.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, right now, this hotel...
Comment: 0,0:39:54.03,0:39:56.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Belongs to someone else.
Comment: 0,0:39:56.16,0:39:59.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The reason I remained as manager\Nwas the kindness of the owner.
Comment: 0,0:39:59.83,0:40:01.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And what happened to your brother?
Comment: 0,0:40:02.21,0:40:03.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After falling into a deep depression, Teruhiko...
Comment: 0,0:40:04.42,0:40:07.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ended up miscalculating on his hang glider, and...
Comment: 0,0:40:11.80,0:40:15.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My brother got too close to a sun called Chizuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Comment: 0,0:40:16.01,0:40:19.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which caused his wings to burn and throw him to the ground.
Comment: 0,0:40:20.02,0:40:22.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then, you held a grudge against Chizuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Comment: 0,0:40:23.02,0:40:26.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Last night, I called Chizuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} to the restaurant.
Comment: 0,0:40:27.48,0:40:30.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if it was only one word, I wanted\Nher to say something to my brother...
Comment: 0,0:40:31.57,0:40:33.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Comment: 0,0:40:33.70,0:40:36.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing comes to mind when that picture.
Comment: 0,0:40:36.99,0:40:38.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How should I know who it is?
Comment: 0,0:40:39.04,0:40:42.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm the older brother of Arimori Teruhiko\Nwho dated you a long time ago.
Comment: 0,0:40:44.12,0:40:46.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My brother died after falling to the ground.
Comment: 0,0:40:48.30,0:40:49.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What are you trying to say?
Comment: 0,0:40:49.88,0:40:52.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I only went out with him because\Nhe wouldn't stop bothering me.
Comment: 0,0:40:53.26,0:40:55.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That person liked me on his own...
Comment: 0,0:40:55.51,0:40:56.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he died on his own.
Comment: 0,0:40:57.35,0:40:59.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not trying to blame you after this long!
Comment: 0,0:40:59.68,0:41:03.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just want you to visit his grave and say one word to him.
Comment: 0,0:41:04.27,0:41:05.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Enough already!
Comment: 0,0:41:05.90,0:41:07.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did I do?
Comment: 0,0:41:07.61,0:41:08.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That doesn't concern me.
Comment: 0,0:41:11.74,0:41:12.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was then...
Comment: 0,0:41:14.36,0:41:16.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That I decided to Chizuru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was to be killed.
Comment: 0,0:41:17.53,0:41:20.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you think your brother is happy now?
Comment: 0,0:41:21.66,0:41:24.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Butterflies are said to be the spirits\Nof those that have passed away.
Comment: 0,0:41:25.12,0:41:26.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To me...
Comment: 0,0:41:26.71,0:41:31.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems it was almost as if your younger brother, in spirit...
Comment: 0,0:41:32.26,0:41:36.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tried to stop you from committing the crime\Nand rested his wings on your shoulder...
Comment: 0,0:43:08.18,0:43:09.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's taking Dad so long?
Comment: 0,0:43:10.65,0:43:12.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where did he go to buy his takoyaki?
Comment: 0,0:43:13.94,0:43:14.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Over there...
Comment: 0,0:43:15.61,0:43:17.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's have tea sometime!
Comment: 0,0:43:17.82,0:43:19.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's have tea!
Comment: 0,0:43:19.49,0:43:20.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We should have tea!
Comment: 0,0:43:23.16,0:43:25.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, with Mouri Kogorou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Comment: 0,0:43:27.08,0:43:27.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Comment: 0,0:43:37.59,0:43:39.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This Icarus...
Comment: 0,0:43:39.26,0:43:40.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is completely hopeless...
